<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Nightmare on YiSheng's secret garden</title><link>https://ezrawu-tw.github.io/en/categories/nightmare/</link><description>Recent content in Nightmare on YiSheng's secret garden</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 19 Nov 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ezrawu-tw.github.io/en/categories/nightmare/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>I feel like I have lost control over myself. What can i do?</title><link>https://ezrawu-tw.github.io/en/posts/always-crazy/</link><pubDate>Wed, 19 Nov 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ezrawu-tw.github.io/en/posts/always-crazy/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;slug: always-crazy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="success-comes-from-pain"&gt;Success comes from pain.&lt;a href="#success-comes-from-pain" class="heading-anchor" aria-label="Link to this section"&gt;&lt;svg class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"&gt;&lt;g fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"&gt;&lt;path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/&gt;&lt;path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;You’ve been wasting time because you’ve been avoiding pain.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There’s no secret shortcut to success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The only thing that produces real results is to work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here’s the question you should ask yourself right now:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Yes, I Once Built a Startup</title><link>https://ezrawu-tw.github.io/en/posts/a-message-from-founder/</link><pubDate>Tue, 18 Nov 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ezrawu-tw.github.io/en/posts/a-message-from-founder/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;slug: a-message-from-founder&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="yes-i-once-built-a-startup"&gt;Yes, I Once Built a Startup&lt;a href="#yes-i-once-built-a-startup" class="heading-anchor" aria-label="Link to this section"&gt;&lt;svg class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"&gt;&lt;g fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"&gt;&lt;path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/&gt;&lt;path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;At the end of 2024, we presented our idea at Microsoft&lt;br&gt;
and stepped into our first real journey.&lt;br&gt;
We visited local shops, spoke with users, and interviewed schools.&lt;br&gt;
We collected meaningful data.&lt;br&gt;
And the adventure began.
